---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
--- 
<Layout>
  <style>
    main {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 72rem; /* 6xl = 72rem */
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      padding: 4rem 1rem; /* py-16 px-4 */
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem; /* text-4xl */
      font-weight: 700; /* font-bold */
      margin-bottom: 3rem; /* mb-12 */
      height: 60px;
      background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #38bdf8, #8b5cf6); /* from-sky-400 to-violet-500 */
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem; /* md:text-5xl */
      }
    }
    
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* grid-cols-1 */
      gap: 2rem; /* gap-8 */
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; /* md:grid-cols-2 */
      }
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 1280px) {
      .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; /* xl:grid-cols-3 */
      }
    }
    
    .card {
      background-color: #1f2937; /* bg-gray-800 */
      border-radius: 0.75rem; /* rounded-xl */
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); /* shadow-xl */
      transition: all 0.3s; /* transition-all duration-300 */
      border: 1px solid #374151; /* border border-gray-700 */
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 360px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    
    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05); /* hover:scale-105 */
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3); /* hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-sky-500/30 */
    }
    
    .image-container {
      height: 20rem; /* h-80 */
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .card-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: top;
      transition: all 0.5s; /* transition-all duration-500 */
    }
    
    .card:hover .card-image {
      transform: scale(1.1); /* group-hover:scale-110 */
    }
    
    .card-content {
      padding: 1.5rem; /* p-6 */
      background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1f2937, #374151); /* from-gray-800 to-gray-700 */
    }
    
    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem; /* text-2xl */
      font-weight: 700; /* font-bold */
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem; /* mb-3 */
      color: #7dd3fc; /* text-sky-300 */
    }
    
    .card:hover .card-title {
      color: #bae6fd; /* group-hover:text-sky-200 */
    }
    
    .card-text {
      color: #e5e7eb; /* text-gray-200 */
    }
    
    .card-link {
      margin-top: 1rem; /* mt-4 */
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      color: #7dd3fc; /* text-sky-300 */
    }
    
    .card:hover .card-link {
      color: #bae6fd; /* group-hover:text-sky-200 */
    }
  </style>
  
  <main>
    <h1>My life, My blog.</h1>
    
    <div class="card-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <a href="/Opposite">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img 
              src="/images/beto.jpg" 
              alt="Descripción de la imagen 1" 
              class="card-image"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2 class="card-title">The Person opposite me.</h2>
            <p class="card-text">
              He is my friend José, but we call him Beto. He is the opposite of me because he is very funny with everything he says and is always doing something, which is the opposite of me since I am very lazy
            </p>
            <div class="card-link">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <a href="/Day">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img 
              src="/images/universidad.jpg" 
              alt="Descripción de la imagen 1" 
              class="card-image"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2 class="card-title">My storyTime.</h2>
            <p class="card-text">
              In this storytime, I talk about my first day at university.
              I tell how my first day was, what I thought was going to happen, and how nervous I felt about starting a new stage in my studies.
            </p>
            <div class="card-link">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <a href="/Me-objects">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img 
              src="/images/Me.jpg" 
              alt="Descripción de la imagen 1" 
              class="card-image"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2 class="card-title">Me in 3 things.</h2>
            <p class="card-text">
              I'm going to explain myself using three things I use daily. These things represent important parts of my routine and help me in my day-to-day life. Through them, you'll get to know a little more about me.
            </p>
            <div class="card-link">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>